The polyester yarn is made in Taiwan, the knit upper

919
00:50:51.714 --> 00:50:55.634
part in China, the EVA foam is produced in Vietnam,

920
00:50:56.694 --> 00:50:59.834
the air unit is manufactured in the United States,

921
00:51:00.474 --> 00:51:04.194
shoelace is produced in China, and final assembly is

