to deal with those.

937
00:51:57.454 --> 00:52:01.134
Some other issues or systems are less clear-cut.

938
00:52:01.894 --> 00:52:05.634
In my submission, for instance, I drew attention to the Kafala

939
00:52:05.694 --> 00:52:07.074
system in the Middle East.

940
00:52:08.554 --> 00:52:12.023
A similar argument will be true for people who work as

941
