and the intuition is not hard to understand.

960
00:53:22.534 --> 00:53:25.594
See, no parent wants children to work.

961
00:53:27.054 --> 00:53:31.014
Children only work when a family is unable to earn

962
00:53:31.074 --> 00:53:32.634
enough for subsistence.

963
00:53:33.994 --> 00:53:37.654
If and when international trade agreements prevent children from

964
00:53:37.714 --> 00:53:41.554
working in Bangladeshi garment factories, for instance, the

965
00:53:41.634 --> 00:53:43.614
children of the needy don't stop working.

966
00:53:44.174 --> 00:53:47.874
They go on to much more precarious work and a much more

967
00:53:47.894 --> 00:53:49.374
precarious existence.

968
00:53:50.694 --> 00:53:54.414
A recent peer-reviewed paper looks at the impact of regional

969
00:53:54.474 --> 00:53:56.334
